<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT72">
<l>illaṟa millēṟ ṟuṟavaṟami leṉṉuñ</l>
<l>collaṟa mallaṉavuñ collalla nallaṟa</l>
<l>māvaṉavum nālvēta māttavamum nāraṇaṉē</l>
<l>yāvatī taṉṟeṉpā rār</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The words that state that the householder dharma, or else, the ascetic dharma</l>
<l rend="indent">is the place [of refuge],</l>
<l>and those that [claim] non-dharmic [means are the refuge] are not words</l>
<l rend="indent">[of authoritative evidence].</l>
<l>Nārāyaṇa is [all] the good dharmas and the great penance of the four Vedas</l>
<l>Who says it is not [so]?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
